answerText: Kingdom of Sweden or Konungariket Sverige[10] Karlstad is on the shores of this largest Swedish lake, which lies northwest of the country's second largest lake, the similarly named Lake Vattern.

question: Question: This country has sovereignty over Gotland and contains the city of Uppsala. For 10 points each: [10] Name this Scandanavian country separated from Finland by the Gulf of Bothnia. Its capital and largest city is built on numerous islands and has many waterways.
